@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xzdsdf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.36 * v0 + 0.74)) - ((v1 + 0.55 + v2 + 0.18) * v0))
    v0 = v0
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.sin(v1 + 0.36) - v2))
    v2 = (0.69 / (wp.sin(v0 + 0.63) + wp.cos(v1 + 0.19)))
    v0 = 0.50
    data[tid] = v0
